class.name: CATICustoIconProduct
class.abstract: Interface to provide icons for the product structure tree.

method.name: GetIconForComponent
method.abstract: Returns the icon to be displayed for a component.

method.name: GetIconForProduct
method.abstract: Returns the icon to be displayed for a product.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddCentralMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether central information mask can be added to the icon.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddContextDesignMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether contextuality information mask can be added to the icon.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddDocMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether document information mask can be added to the icon.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddFlexibleDesignMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether flexible design information mask can be added to the icon.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddGearsMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether gears mask can be added to the icon.

method.name: IsPossibleToAddRepMask
method.abstract: Indicates whether representation information mask can be added to the icon.

class.name: CATIPrdHandleImpactsOnInstance
class.abstract: Interface to rename a Product Instance and manage the impacts.

method.name: RenameInstance
method.abstract: Renames a Product Instance and reconnect pointing elements.

class.name: CATIPrdHandleImpactsOnReference
class.abstract: Interface to rename a Publication and manage the impacts.

method.name: RenamePublication
method.abstract: Renames a Publication and reconnect its pointing elements.

class.name: CATIPrdPLMPersistency
class.abstract: Provide PDM information for product document.

method.name: get_PersistencyHost
method.abstract: Returns the type of the PDM server that manage the persistency of the document.

method.name: get_PersistencyMode
method.abstract: Returns the Persistency mode associated to the document.

enum.name: PersistencyHost
enum.abstract: Type of the PDM server that hosts the document.

enum.name: PersistencyMode
enum.abstract: Modes available to store a document into the selected PMD server.

class.name: CATIPrdTransactionalEventMgt
class.abstract: Interface allowing a transactional management for move operations.
